      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showLineNumbersOnHover": false
        },
        "content": "# Chat21 Message Metrics Dashboard\n\nThis dashboard provides insights into the outgoing message flow within the Chat21 server. All time-series metrics are aggregated with a **1-minute resolution** using the `increase()` function, showing the exact number of messages sent within each minute.\n\n### Metrics Explained:\n\n- **Messages per Project per Time**: Tracks the volume of messages for each project. Use the `Project ID` filter to focus on specific projects.\n- **Messages Today (24h)**: A summary of the total messages sent across all (or filtered) projects in the last 24 hours.\n- **Messages by IP Address**: Monitors message activity from different source IP addresses. Helps in identifying high-traffic sources or potential anomalies.\n- **Messages by Project and IP Address**: Provides a granular view of which project is receiving messages from which IP address. Useful for debugging and traffic analysis.\n- **Messages by Topic**: Shows the distribution of messages across various AMQP/MQTT topics (e.g., direct messages, group updates, etc.).\n\n### Filtering:\n\nUse the dropdowns at the top to filter data by **Project ID** or **IP Address**. Multiple selections are supported.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Dashboard Description",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
